TouchGrass 

i created this simple python app to remind me to take a break and not staring the monitor too much
not something fancy, just click and run

## How to Use
1. Select your work duration
2. Click "Start Timer"
3. Work
4. It will play a windows notification sound when the timer is over
5. Take a break,then restart it

## Installation
1. git clone https://github.com/bAmeGR/TouchGrass.git
2. cd TouchGrass
3. Python 3.7+ installed
4. Install required dependencies:
5. pip install plyer
6. python main.py
